# Aspire Leadership Program | Week 7: Communicating for Impact

This directory contains the coursework, assignments, case study reflections, and peer discussion notes for **Week 7 (Communicating for Impact)** of the Aspire Leadership Program. The core focus of this module is synthesizing project proposals (from Weeks 4 and 5) into compelling narratives to build trust, secure stakeholder buy-in, and maximize project impact.

